<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看<tag a="110" b="0" />
這就是流星雨喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />速度快到來不及許願呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="8" />的夜空<delay20 />
滿載大家的願望，
閃閃發亮呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
未來也會充滿笑容<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />剛剛流星對我眨眼睛了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天空出現了一座美麗的彩虹橋呢。<delay frames="40" />
感覺今天也會有好事發生<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果走過這座彩虹橋，<delay20 />
會抵達什麼地方呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我無法將視線從彩虹移開，<delay frames="40" />
總覺得彩虹會在我移開視線的瞬間<delay20 />
消失無蹤<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對我來說，彩虹是<delay20 />
身穿七彩禮服的女神喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天空裡的彩虹真令人嘆為觀止呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能看到普通的彩虹就算Lucky了，<delay20 />沒想到有機會
遇見雙彩虹，真是Very Lucky呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真讓人猶豫，<delay20 />
不知道該看哪一邊的彩虹<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />只有現在花心應該沒關係吧。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然那邊的彩虹很美，<delay20 />
但這邊的彩虹也很不錯呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我沒有辦法做出選擇啦。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然常常有人將極光比喻為光之帷幕，<delay20 />
但看起來真的就像窗簾呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想在房間裡放這種擺設。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透光的質感真驚人～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道能不能<delay20 />
用極光做晚宴服呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我認為，因為這景象只有現在能看到，<delay20 />
所以才極具價值。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要趁現在把它深深烙印在<delay20 />
名為心靈的底片上<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那飛機雲<delay20 />
會延伸到什麼地方呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺追著那朵雲去旅行<delay20 />
也不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飛機雲<delay20 />
就像在天空畫畫一樣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也好想在這寬廣無垠的<delay20 />
天空畫布上作畫<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能用飛機雲<delay8 />
傳達求愛的訊息，<delay20 />
一定很浪漫呢～
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />
我現在沒有對象就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在賞月啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
因為剛剛不經意抬頭一看，<delay20 />
發現月色實在是太美麗了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道現在是不是有人<delay20 />
也在某個地方看著這月色呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />如果有一天，
能與那個人相遇就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />月夜總是讓我感到疼痛難耐<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
此刻將我真實的面貌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔唔唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我亂說的啦～<delay8 />哈哈～！</message>
</msbt>